title: E31 Pregnancy with Heidi Murkoff
itunes:title: Pregnancy with Heidi Murkoff
description:
In this episode, the team discusses pregnancy with author of "What to Expect When You're Expecting", Heidi Murkoff.


Follow Heidi on social media (@heidimurkoff) or go to her website at www.whattoexpect.com


You can also listen to her podcast "What to Expect" or download the What to Expec app on the Apple App Store or Google Play Store.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
